{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WcpTnchkrqV8NLRGpTBg8v","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018Hj6NPuhRAHK2XWb3sJK33","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Roasted Brussels Sprouts.generated.18.txt","content":"ROASTED BRUSSELS SPROUTS\n\nThere's something magical about roasting Brussels sprouts. When my grandmother first taught me this recipe,\nshe insisted that the secret wasn't fancy ingredients—it was letting the sprouts caramelize slowly in the oven\nuntil their outer leaves turned crispy and brown. Every family gathering, she'd have two large sheet pans roasting\naway. The aroma would fill the entire house, and by the time guests arrived, half the batch was already gone.\nThis simple preparation brings out the natural sweetness of the sprouts in a way that steaming or boiling never could.\n\nIngredients:\n- 800g Brussels sprouts, halved lengthwise\n- 3 tablespoons olive oil\n- 1 teaspoon sea salt\n- 1/2 teaspoon black pepper\n- 1/2 teaspoon garlic powder\n- 1/4 teaspoon red pepper flakes\n- 2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar\n- 2 tablespoons grated Parmesan cheese\n- Fresh thyme for garnish\n\nInstructions:\n1. Preheat oven to 220°C (425°F).\n2. Toss Brussels sprouts with olive oil, salt, pepper, garlic powder, and red pepper flakes.\n3. Spread in single layer on baking sheet, cut-side down.\n4. Roast 25-30 minutes, shaking pan halfway through, until golden brown.\n5. Drizzle with balsamic vinegar and toss gently.\n6. Transfer to serving plate, sprinkle with Parmesan and fresh thyme.\n7. Serve warm as a side dish.\n\nServes 4-6 as a side dish or light appetizer. Perfect alongside roasted chicken or fish.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":63871,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":63871},"output_tokens":7,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e799c0bb-71c9-46cb-a2f5-0d09a4801c74","uuid":"a796612a-f341-404c-8412-206f6288175b"}
