{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WcpTnchkrqV8NLRGpTBg8v","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FPmBwX2aMeueNr6AELoHni","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Barszcz.generated.18.txt","content":"BARSZCZ\n\nGrowing up in Warsaw, my family made barszcz for every important occasion. My mother would spend hours\ntending the pot, ensuring the beets released their deep crimson color into the broth. She always said that\nthe key was patience—rushing the beets would result in a pale, weak broth that didn't honor the vegetable.\nThis recipe comes from her collection of handwritten cards, worn and stained from decades of use in the kitchen.\nIt's traditionally served at Christmas Eve supper, in small cups, often with tiny savory pastries floating inside.\n\nIngredients:\n- 1 kg fresh beets, peeled and cut into chunks\n- 2 liters beef or vegetable stock\n- 1 large onion, quartered\n- 3 cloves garlic, smashed\n- 1 bay leaf\n- 3 whole cloves\n- 3-4 tablespoons red wine vinegar\n- 1 tablespoon sugar\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- Fresh dill for garnish\n\nInstructions:\n1. Place beets, onion, garlic, bay leaf, and cloves in large pot with stock.\n2. Bring to boil, then reduce heat and simmer gently for 60 minutes.\n3. Strain broth through fine sieve, pressing gently on vegetables.\n4. Return to pot and season with vinegar, sugar, salt, and pepper.\n5. Heat through and serve in small cups.\n6. Garnish with fresh dill.\n\nTraditionally served with uszka (small mushroom dumplings).\nServes 6-8 as a starter course.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":63871,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":63871},"output_tokens":7,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e799c0bb-71c9-46cb-a2f5-0d09a4801c74","uuid":"5846b4b8-fe48-468c-ac77-37df39c355b1"}
