{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WcpTnchkrqV8NLRGpTBg8v","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Gf7fPVPPS9N9k7Ayd7F3PH","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Salmon Teriyaki.generated.18.txt","content":"SALMON TERIYAKI\n\nI discovered this dish during a trip to Tokyo, where a small izakaya near Shibuya served it as their signature preparation.\nThe chef explained that the magic happens in the glaze—the way soy sauce, mirin, and sake come together creates a glossy coating\nthat caramelizes in the pan. Back home, I've adapted it slightly using what's available locally, but the essence remains the same.\nNow my dinner guests always ask for this recipe, and I've made it so many times I could probably prepare it with my eyes closed.\nThe balance of sweet, salty, and umami is what makes this dish truly memorable.\n\nIngredients:\n- 4 salmon fillets (150g each), skin on\n- 1/4 cup soy sauce\n- 2 tablespoons mirin\n- 1 tablespoon sake (or dry sherry)\n- 1 tablespoon honey\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n- 1 teaspoon fresh ginger, grated\n- 1 tablespoon vegetable oil\n- Sesame seeds and scallions for garnish\n- Steamed rice for serving\n\nInstructions:\n1. Combine soy sauce, mirin, sake, honey, garlic, and ginger in a small bowl.\n2. Heat oil in large skillet over medium-high heat.\n3. Place salmon skin-side up in pan and cook 3-4 minutes until skin is crispy.\n4. Flip salmon and pour teriyaki mixture around fillets.\n5. Cook 3-4 minutes more until sauce thickens and salmon is cooked through.\n6. Transfer salmon to plates, spoon remaining sauce over top.\n7. Garnish with sesame seeds and sliced scallions.\n8. Serve immediately with steamed rice.\n\nServes 4. Also wonderful with roasted vegetables on the side.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":63871,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":63871},"output_tokens":7,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e799c0bb-71c9-46cb-a2f5-0d09a4801c74","uuid":"9e347f07-6fab-452f-b14a-00b2c62ab22a"}
